duties_responsibilities.duty: Staffing all necessary resource requests for the Consulting organization.
Partnering with Delivery Managers and Operation Analysts to staff the scheduled projects.
Collaborating with project managers and consultants on scheduling projects.
Managing the resourcing request queue and reviewing statements of work.
Identifying over or underutilized associates and highlighting future conflicting events.
Working on scheduling and troubleshooting project schedules.

education_certification.credential: Bachelor's degree or equivalent relevant work experience
